  "detailed_description": "<h1>Introduction of the Team</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/291ed744ba7d2e65be5c3ebf5cc06ce5.avif?t=1714031019\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/66fb886562f8b3153e2020fb038d5c3b.avif?t=1714031019\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/f46b596b3e2b68811e401ae7e3bdd4b4.avif?t=1714031019\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/236deaf113f7962790ceeab272639030.avif?t=1714031019\" width=616 height=308 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Traditional JRPG game, experience a fantasy story! More interesting adventures await you to discover surprises and encounters.<br><br>The “Border Mountains” is the first work developed by Hercules Game Studio. The game features classic role-playing and turn-based combat. Defeat enemies on your journey and uncover the truth of the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/ac3ae221e58d664c18de3c43648e3973.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/ac3ae221e58d664c18de3c43648e3973.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/ac3ae221e58d664c18de3c43648e3973.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Experience the combat strategies brought by different professions and skills. Every battle is different because of your decisions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/49b48270e9a196814b6957bea795ba1e.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/49b48270e9a196814b6957bea795ba1e.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/49b48270e9a196814b6957bea795ba1e.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Set off from the foot of the mountain, explore the dangerous wilderness and cave mazes, unravel the traps set by enemies!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Delve into the shadows of the mountains, discover the truth of the story, and defeat powerful bosses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Face different enemies and challenges with the protagonist team during the adventure, and grow together with them!\"",
