tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/10061cb93ce43af549f09872a0b3aed3.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Delve into the shadows of the mountains, discover the truth of the story, and defeat powerful bosses!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.poster.avif?t=1714031019\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.webm?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2865330/extras/92ef2ec9a26122cc0dab1250ff75c6ac.mp4?t=1714031019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Face different enemies and challenges with the protagonist team during the adventure, and grow together with them!\"",
